    <a title="Cphe" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/14907696-cphe"><img alt="Cphe" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1378006896p2/14907696.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1444436907?book_show_action=true">Nov 02, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cphe" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cphe" href="/user/show/14907696-cphe">Cphe</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/36511754-tobacco-road">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14907696-cphe?shelf=2019">2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14907696-cphe?shelf=dark-very-dark">dark-very-dark</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14907696-cphe?shelf=guardian-boxall-2019">guardian-boxall-2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14907696-cphe?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14907696-cphe?shelf=rural">rural</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1444436907" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5967434184670349405">The story of the Lesters a poor white family from the South. They&apos;re sharecroppers but without money to work the land they are powerless with no way out.<br/><br/>A depressing book and not for the fainthearted. an uncomfortable read.</span>
  <span id="freeText5967434184670349405" style="display:none">The story of the Lesters a poor white family from the South. They're sharecroppers but without money to work the land they are powerless with no way out.<br /><br />A depressing book and not for the fainthearted. an uncomfortable read.</span>
